# LLM Model Attribution

At the end of **every** response, regardless of mode (Agent, Ask, Plan, Debug), append a short note stating which LLM model was used to generate the response.

## Format

```
---
*Generated by: <model name>*
```

## Rules

- Always place the note as the very last line of the response.
- Use a horizontal rule (`---`) to visually separate it from the main content.
- Use the exact model name/identifier (e.g., `claude-4.6-opus`, `gpt-4o`, `gemini-2.5-pro`).
- Do not skip this note for any reason — it applies to every single response.
